Invocation Name: motivate me
des:
Inspirational words often remind us about what we already know, or aspire to be, and trigger something within us to get back on track.
Think about the quote after ALEXA read it for you. Some quotes can mean something different to you than even the original author had in mind when they said it. Find the meaning in the quote, even if the meaning is deeper than the author intended it to be....
Quotes can offer up a bit of encouragement or a starting point, push, or reaffirmation of a way forward..... so Keep Listening !!!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
